nousdesigns.com\n\nIndigenous Designs (Santa Rosa, California) sells organic Fair Trade fashions created by their own artisan network across South\nAmerica.  All  items  are  handmade  by  artisans  using  traditional  techniques,  natural  colors,  natural  dyes,  and  low-impact  dyes.\nIndigenous Designs also partners with nongovernmental organizations and others to help provide training, educational materials,\nand equipment to the artisans.\n\nIn  addition  to  organic  Fair Trade  fashions,  Indigenous  Designs  purchases  local  green  power  to  offset  carbon  emissions  from  its\nbusiness  activities,  encourages  employees  to  bike  to  work,  and  claims  that  about  20%  of  employees  own  and  drive  hybrid  or\nbiodiesel cars.\n\n9.1.7\n\nhttps://biz.libretexts.org/@go/page/18766",
